# Flutter Architecture

- Keep app bootstrapping in `lib/main.dart` and app composition in `lib/app/`.
- Organize user-facing work by feature under `lib/features/<feature>/`.
- Use `domain`, `data`, and `presentation` boundaries for features that have real business logic.
- Keep shared UI in `lib/shared/widgets/` and platform/service code in `lib/core/`.
- Prefer small widgets, explicit dependencies, and feature-local providers.
